        {
            "title": "歐洲股市上漲 投資者向防禦股輪動",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"1017\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/M6wS63bKG8XTBKncGItVhg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEwMTc-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/523f3f32ac2972ac2aced4a8815b6caa\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐洲股市上漲，醫療健保和房地產等防禦性板塊跑贏，投資者仍擔憂人工智能的影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲斯托克600指數收漲，銀行和保險股也走高，而受金屬價格下跌影響，礦業股表現最為滯後。油價下跌，拖累能源股走低，有跡象表明美國與伊朗在核談判中取得進展。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">面對美國科技股動盪帶來的衝擊，以及對人工智能將顛覆軟件行業的擔憂，投資者轉向歐洲市場以尋求避風港。美國銀行最新的基金經理調查顯示，越來越多的投資者認為歐洲股市結構性跑輸的局面已經結束。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-bb13d80b-9699-37ef-9e41-8bac3f82b395-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Andreas Bruckner牽頭的美國銀行策略師引用的數據顯示，高達74%的投資者認為，隨著德國財政刺激措施提振宏觀經濟數據，歐洲經濟成長將在短期內加速，這一比例創紀錄新高。他們寫道，預期歐洲周期股上行空間大於防禦股的投資者比例接近一年來的最高水平。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"1017\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/t6yaZoBXs5VTylve1Vtr_A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEwMTc-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/62a1b485399458fdb84927b8154418c6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「美國長周末和春節帶來的微弱流動性造成了艱難的技術面背景，地緣政治風險情緒也已蔓延至市場，」CG Asset Management的投資組合經理Emma Moriarty表示，「但全球金融環境趨於寬鬆的預期表明，歐洲企業的經營環境可能正在變得更加有利。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在英國，出口導向型富時100指數上漲，英鎊走弱，此前發布的經濟數據顯示失業率升至近五年來的最高水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，Aroundtown躍升，Viceroy Research表示它看好這家房地產公司，稱其股票「被嚴重低估」。銅礦商Antofagasta下跌，該公司的盈利和派息不及一些分析師預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">凱愛瑞集團下跌，這家愛爾蘭食品生產商在歐洲、中東和非洲以及亞太市場的成長低於預期，匯率波動也帶來了不利影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題European Stocks Advance as Investors Rotate Into Defensives</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Jan-Patrick Barnert、Sagarika Jaisinghani、Charles Riley、Michael Msika.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2-%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E5%90%91%E9%98%B2%E7%A6%A6%E8%82%A1%E8%BC%AA%E5%8B%95-180412215.html",
