        {
            "title": "美國住宅建築商信心指數跌至五個月低點 受可負擔性困擾拖累",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"National Association of Home Builders/Wells Fargo\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"438\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/o7SgMDNy9x_.nD2lRXmlYA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQzOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/d3c4ae68e44c7e7e9f84ad356fca3b51\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">National Association of Home Builders/Wells Fargo</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國住宅<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:建築商;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/建築商\">建築商</a>信心本月再度下滑，持續的負擔能力擔憂以及高企的建築成本構成拖累。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國全國住宅建築商協會（NAHB）和富國銀行聯合發布的市場狀況指數2月降至36，為去年9月以來最低水平。這一讀數幾乎低於彭博調查的所有經濟學家的預期。指數低於50意味著認為市場狀況不佳的建築商多於認為狀況良好的。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"438\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gc0ZVGxbfZmLmq5RLYlqkg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQzOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3fb20daeeec1970c8824a01bea518867\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「儘管大多數建築商仍在提供降價在內的購房激勵措施，但許多潛在買家仍選擇觀望，」NAHB主席、來自北卡羅來納州的建築商Buddy Hughes在聲明中表示。「雖然新建住宅需求走弱，但由於家庭流動性不足，翻修需求依然穩健。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-95643515-4529-3d74-b00d-78dce39ef8d8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對數百萬潛在購房者而言，負擔能力仍是難題，並持續制約房地產市場。儘管抵押貸款利率接近逾一年來的最低水平，但仍是2021年大部分時間水平的兩倍左右。建築商不得不通過降價和提供激勵措施應對。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">NAHB稱，本月仍有高達65%的建築商提供銷售激勵措施，與上月持平。與此同時，報告降價的建築商比例在2月降至36%，為去年5月以來最低。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在NAHB指數的分項中，未來六個月銷售預期指標降至46，連續第二個月低於50。當前銷售指標和潛在買家流量指標已至少一年低於這一關鍵水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Homebuilder Sentiment Dips to Five-Month Low on Affordability</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Chris Middleton.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%BB%BA%E7%AF%89%E5%95%86%E4%BF%A1%E5%BF%83%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E8%B7%8C%E8%87%B3%E4%BA%94%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E4%BD%8E%E9%BB%9E-%E5%8F%97%E5%8F%AF%E8%B2%A0%E6%93%94%E6%80%A7%E5%9B%B0%E6%93%BE%E6%8B%96%E7%B4%AF-153414907.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-18 01:23:56",
